        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Montana Sportsmen Conservation Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill releases the Middle Fork Judith, Hoodoo Mountain, and Wales Creek wilderness study areas from further study for wilderness designation. &lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
